graph LR
    KubeRay["KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.4.2"]

    %% External Dependencies (Required)
    KubeRay -->|platform| K8s["Kubernetes 1.24+<br/>(Required)"]

    %% External Dependencies (Optional)
    KubeRay -.->|certificate mgmt| CertManager["cert-manager 1.0+<br/>(Optional)"]
    KubeRay -.->|ingress| OpenShiftRoute["OpenShift Route API 4.x<br/>(Optional)"]
    KubeRay -.->|advanced ingress| GatewayAPI["Gateway API v1/v1beta1<br/>(Optional)"]
    KubeRay -.->|gang scheduling| Volcano["Volcano Scheduler<br/>(Optional)"]
    KubeRay -.->|batch scheduling| Yunikorn["Yunikorn Scheduler<br/>(Optional)"]
    KubeRay -.->|job queue| Kueue["Kueue<br/>(Optional)"]

    %% OpenShift Integration
    KubeRay -->|webhook certs| OSServiceCA["OpenShift Service CA<br/>(OpenShift)"]
    KubeRay -->|auth integration| OSAuth["OpenShift OAuth API<br/>(OpenShift)"]

    %% Monitoring
    Prometheus["Prometheus"] -->|scrapes metrics| KubeRay

    %% Managed Resources
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| RayCluster["Ray Clusters<br/>(Head + Workers)"]
    KubeRay -->|creates/manages| K8sResources["Kubernetes Resources<br/>Pods, Services, ConfigMaps,<br/>Secrets, NetworkPolicies"]

    %% Integration Points (not dependencies)
    Dashboard["ODH Dashboard"] -.->|optional UI| KubeRay
    Pipelines["Data Science Pipelines"] -.->|job submission| RayCluster

    %% Styling
    style KubeRay fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% Required External
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Optional External
    style CertManager fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style OpenShiftRoute fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style GatewayAPI fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Volcano fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Yunikorn fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Kueue fill:#ccc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% OpenShift
    style OSServiceCA fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style OSAuth fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Internal ODH
    style Prometheus fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Pipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Managed
    style RayCluster fill:#bd10e0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style K8sResources fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
